yingyinNormal.en: We'll tell Old Nick that because of the power cut, you got so cold, that you got a fever.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们跟老尼克说，因为断电你着凉了，发烧了。

yingyinNormal.en: When you get a virus, you get a fever. That's the human body raising its core temperature to kill the virus.
yingyinNormal.zh: 当你感染上病毒，你就会发烧。这是人体提高自己的体温来杀死病毒。

yingyinNormal.en: Hey, Claire. What's up? My fever, you orange jackass. Oh. Okay. So, obviously, you have my cold now.
yingyinNormal.zh: 克莱尔，怎么了？我发烧了，你个带病的混蛋。好吧，显然你传染上了我的感冒。

yingyinNormal.en: What? You hold my hand, you kiss my mouth, but you draw the line at 102 fever? What happened to our love?
yingyinNormal.zh: 怎么？你牵我的手，亲我的嘴就行，但我发烧到39度就过界了吗？我们的爱情怎么了？

yingyinNormal.en: The pain in my mouth when I had braces. I can remember the feeling of your hand on my forehead when I ran a fever.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我带着牙套时，嘴巴所感受到的疼痛，我还记得发烧的时候你掌心放在我额头的感觉。

yingyinNormal.en: Planet Earth works the same way: Global warming is the fever. Mankind is the virus. We are making our planet sick. A cull is our only hope.
yingyinNormal.zh: 地球也是这样的，温室效应就是发烧。人类就是病毒，我们让我们的星球病了。优胜劣汰是唯一的希望。

yingyinNormal.en: I would just say: watch out for signs of infection, fever, redness.
yingyinNormal.zh: 就是要注意有没有感染，发热，红肿什么的。
yingyinNormal.videoNameEn: 《Rise of the Planet of the Apes》

yingyinNormal.en: The fever. The rage. The feeling of powerlessness. It turns good men cruel.
yingyinNormal.zh: 怒火，狂暴，无力的感觉，能让好人变得残酷。

yingyinNormal.en: Then why is she going to a play? You know, starve a fever, go to a play for a cold.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那她为什么要去看演出？你知道的，感冒想退烧，就要去看演出。

yingyinNormal.en: It's scarlet fever. He'll be in bed for several months, at least. Complete isolation.
yingyinNormal.zh: 是猩红热。他至少需要卧床几个月。完全隔离。

yingyinNormal.en: Yeah, she's been in there all day, high fever, a nose problem. Phlegm. Phlegm. Phlegm.
yingyinNormal.zh: 对啊，她整天都在房里，发高烧，鼻塞，痰痰痰痰痰。

yingyinNormal.en: Yeah, even if it turns out you don't have Dengue fever, they still let you take a lollipop.
yingyinNormal.zh: 就算检查结果显示你没得登革热，你还是可以拿根棒棒糖。

yingyinNormal.en: Maggie, dear, there are people in there suffering. I can bring their fever down and keep them stable.
yingyinNormal.zh: 玛吉，亲爱的，那里有很多人饱受煎熬，我能帮他们退烧，维持性命。

yingyinNormal.en: Well, as I predicted, I am sick. My fever has been tracking up exponentially since 2:00 a.m., and I am producing sputum at an alarming rate.
yingyinNormal.zh: 是这样，跟我预测的如出一辙，我病了。我的体温从凌晨两点开始就呈指数曲线上升，而且我痰中含血量惊人地高。

yingyinNormal.en: I think it's weird you don't like cutesy considering half your clients at the grammys looked like they just stepped out of a my little pony fever dream.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我觉得你不喜欢卖萌这点真的很奇怪，因为你旗下一半出席格莱美奖的客户看上去像是刚从我的幼稚痴梦里走出来的。

yingyinNormal.en: In fact, there are many reported cases of farts spreading Streptococcus pyogenes, a pathogen that can cause tonsillitis, scarlet fever, heart disease and even flesh eating disease.
yingyinNormal.zh: 许多已通报案例指出放屁会传播化脓性链球菌，这种病原体会导致扁桃腺炎、猩红热、心脏病跟食肉细菌感染。
